'''卡亞'''（Kaya）是[[南蘇丹|南蘇丹]]南端的小鎮，由[[中赤道省|中赤道省]]負責管轄，位於與[[烏干達|烏干達]]接壤的邊界上，處於首都[[朱巴|朱巴]]以南約220公里<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Sudan_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Morobo%20(Al%20Wilayah%20al%20Istiwa'iyah)&toplace=Juba%20()%20(Airport)%20&fromlat=3.6919444&tolat=4.872006&fromlng=30.7763889&tolng=31.601117 |title=Map Showing Kaya And Juba With Distance Marker |access-date=2011-09-11 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303235518/http://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Sudan_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Morobo%20(Al%20Wilayah%20al%20Istiwa'iyah)&toplace=Juba%20()%20(Airport)%20&fromlat=3.6919444&tolat=4.872006&fromlng=30.7763889&tolng=31.601117 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是繁忙的商業中心，販商來自南蘇丹、烏干達和[[剛果民主共和國|剛果民主共和國]]。

